# Butter Chicken

Based on [https://twosleevers.com/instant-pot-butter-chicken/](https://twosleevers.com/instant-pot-butter-chicken) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20260115133819/https://twosleevers.com/instant-pot-butter-chicken/))

